Since its inception in 2004, MHVillage has grown to become the nation’s largest website exclusively dedicated to manufactured housing. Millions of homebuyers shop MHVillage.com, and we currently have more than 22,898 homes available for sale and 4,342 homes available for rent on our site. Which means if you want to reach consumers interested in your homes, communities, or products and services, you’ve come to the right place.
Because of our size and focus, MHVillage gives you unequaled reach. With our proven ability to drive qualified traffic to homeowners and manufactured housing professionals alike, we offer the best programs for selling homes and generating new business.
MHVillage offers a unique, engaged audience that is interested in manufactured housing as a potential solution for their affordable housing needs. We continually rank among the highest results for manufactured home related searches online. And unlike general real estate websites, you’re not competing against other housing types eager to steal away your best prospects.
If you’re not on MHVillage, the most active website for manufactured housing, you’re simply missing out.
If you have a question, comment, feedback, or suggestion, we would love to hear from you! Please select an option below to contact us.
